                        <interp inst="t18360404-name-217" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM EBBEN</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a watch and clock maker, and live in High-street, Islington Two spoons were offered to me, one by the prisoner and the other by Davison—I will not he certain what I gave the prisoner for it, but he tells me 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>4<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.—it was worth 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>—I have weighted it and I think I must have given him 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.—I asked where he came from—I think he said No. 1.</p>
               <p>
